title: Iron Maiden SINGLES DISCOGRAPHY (live, DVD and vinyl)
description:
This is my collection of Iron Maiden SINGLES DISCOGRAPHY.
I've collected all this since I'm a fan of IM.

Here are all studio, vinyl and DVD singles. ALL 55 of them.
All info is collected from IM official website few years ago.
Recent releases info (from 2008 and onwards) are from wiki.

All covers are in ID3 Tag. All covers are in sizes between 800px and 1500 I think.


A picture is worth a thousand words.
  <a href="
http://img837.imageshack.us/img837/435/92io.png" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW">
http://img837.imageshack.us/img837/435/92io.png</a>



Note:

These are ONLY official releases.
I repeat, informations are "copied" from OFFICIAL IM website....long time ago.

Quality of tracks is MP3, VBR, between 225kbps and 320kbps, around 260kbps.
I love good ol' 2-channel stereo. ;)


ENJOY and SEED!!!

P.S. Don't forget to tell me what you think. ;)
